<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

<title>Transcriptomics | PanorOmics</title>

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}

body{
  background:#020817;
  color:white;
  font-family:Inter,Arial,sans-serif;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}

.page{
  padding:90px 7% 70px;
}

.back{
  color:#3b82f6;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-weight:700;
}

.hero{
  margin-top:48px;
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:42px;
  align-items:center;
}

h1{
  font-size:clamp(3rem,5vw,5rem);
  line-height:.95;
  letter-spacing:-.05em;
}

h1 span{color:#3b82f6}

p{
  margin-top:22px;
  color:#cbd5e1;
  font-size:1rem;
  line-height:1.75;
  max-width:720px;
}

.video-box,
.image-box{
  border-radius:26px;
  overflow:hidden;
  border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.14);
  box-shadow:0 0 70px rgba(37,99,235,.14);
}

video,img{
  width:100%;
  display:block;
}

.section{
  padding:56px 0;
}

h2{
  font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3.4rem);
  margin-bottom:20px;
  line-height:1.05;
}

h2 span{color:#3b82f6}

.grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(230px,1fr));
  gap:20px;
  margin-top:30px;
}

.card{
  background:rgba(8,15,35,.72);
  border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.12);
  border-radius:22px;
  padding:24px;
}

.card h3{
  color:#3b82f6;
  margin-bottom:12px;
}

.card p{
  margin-top:0;
  font-size:.95rem;
  color:#94a3b8;
}

@media(max-width:900px){
  .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .page{padding:80px 22px 60px}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<main class="page">

  <a class="back" href="/">← Back to PanorOmics</a>

  <section class="hero">

    <div>
      <h1>Transcriptomics: <span>Dynamic Gene Expression</span></h1>

      <p>
        Transcriptomics studies the complete set of RNA transcripts produced by the genome.
        It reveals how genes are activated, regulated, and translated into biological
        function across cells, tissues, disease states, and environmental conditions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="video-box">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
        <source src="/3_Transcriptomics Dynamic gene expression.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
    </div>

  </section>

  <section class="section">

    <h2>What is <span>Transcriptomics?</span></h2>

    <div class="image-box">
      <img src="/1_Transcriptomics Picture.png" alt="Transcriptomics overview infographic" />
    </div>

  </section>

  <section class="section">

    <h2>Core Areas</h2>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h3>RNA Expression</h3><p>Measuring gene activity through RNA abundance.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>RNA-seq</h3><p>Sequencing transcripts to profile biological states.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Alternative Splicing</h3><p>Understanding how one gene can generate multiple RNA isoforms.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Non-coding RNA</h3><p>Studying regulatory RNAs including lncRNA, miRNA, and other ncRNA classes.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Single-cell Transcriptomics</h3><p>Resolving gene expression at individual-cell resolution.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Systems Regulation</h3><p>Connecting RNA activity to pathways, networks, and phenotype.</p></div>
    </div>

  </section>

</main>

</body>
</html>
